song.title: Saga
song.info: This time - romantic ballad. You know, I like celtic music very much! Btw, the tune was planned as a Looker House contribution to The Party 6, but Zinko//LKR, who had to bring it there, didn't appear on irc in the right time, and seems like that mail had not reached him! So I had to make a single release on PeeCee (and that's not so bad :).
